🛠️ Task 1 – View Running Processes

All processes:

ps -ef

User processes:

ps -u $USER

Process tree:

pstree
🛠️ Task 2 – Monitor Processes

Interactive:

top

Better UI:

htop

Install:

sudo apt install htop
🛠️ Task 3 – Find Process

Find SSH:

pgrep ssh

Find Nginx:

pgrep nginx

Search:

ps -ef | grep nginx
🛠️ Task 4 – Kill Processes

Kill by PID:

kill 1234

Force kill:

kill -9 1234

Kill by name:

pkill nginx

Kill all:

killall nginx
🛠️ Task 5 – Background Jobs

Start:

sleep 300 &

View jobs:

jobs

Bring to foreground:

fg %1

Background again:

Ctrl + Z
bg %1
🛠️ Task 6 – nohup

Run even after logout:

nohup python3 app.py &

Output:

nohup.out
🛠️ Task 7 – Process Priority

Run low priority:

nice -n 10 python3 app.py

Change priority:

renice 15 PID

View:

ps -eo pid,ni,comm
🛠️ Task 8 – Open Files

View files opened by process:

lsof -p PID

Who is using port 8080?

sudo lsof -i :8080
🛠️ Task 9 – Trace System Calls

Install:

sudo apt install strace

Trace:

strace ls

Attach:

strace -p PID
