🔥 Production Scenario
Problem

A Java application is consuming 100% CPU on a production server.

Investigation

Find the process:

top

or

ps -eo pid,%cpu,comm --sort=-%cpu | head

Inspect the process:

ps -fp <PID>

Check open files:

lsof -p <PID>

Trace activity:

strace -p <PID>

Reduce priority (temporary):

sudo renice 10 <PID>

If the process is hung and cannot recover:

sudo kill <PID>

Use kill -9 only if a normal kill does not terminate the process.

